ai-patthana16.92:0.2_0: Having given the immaculateness of the Dhamma
ai-patthana16.92:0.3_0: Transmigration, always on the eyes that are made,
ai-patthana16.92:1.1_0: One who has not dedicated to the untroubled and not gives rise to satisfaction, nor does relying on that account.
ai-patthana16.92:2.1_0: One thing doesn’t give rise to unprotected bathing, for extremely knowing this, doesn’t give rise to a cause or reason.
ai-patthana16.92:2.1_2: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
